nk Reports Highest-Ever Annual Profit For a Japanese Company. Colonial Face=
s Deadline to Decide on  Hacked Pipeline Restart. Companies prepare share b=
uyback bonanza as profits surge.=C2=A0F.B.I. Asking Questions After a Pensi=
on Fund Aimed High and Fell Short. Greensill Capital Is Target of U.K. Gove=
rnment Probe. The  Options Market May Be Fueling the Turbulence in Tech Sha=
res. U.S. DOJ Remits $452 Million of  Seized 1MDB Funds to Malaysia. Fangs =
and tentacles: rarely seen deep sea fish washes up on California beach.If y=
